RemoteBackup version 0.01

For testing, place the id_rsa file in your ~/.ssh/ direcotry.

See the configuration file ./config/example.xml for how to
set up machines, directories, and databases to be backed up.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the
following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

Moose
XML::Simple

